messageBody:
I just noticed that Omniglot (http://www.omniglot.com) has recently
added some wood carvings by Edoardo Triscoli in different scripts. One
of these is in Quikscript:
http://www.omniglot.com/gallery/pirografia/index.php?start=7

It may not be the best of his work, but I think it's certainly worth
notice.
